org.keycloak.connections.mongo.impl.context

Class TransactionMongoStoreInvocationContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.keycloak.connections.mongo.impl.context.TransactionMongoStoreInvocationContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MongoStoreInvocationContext

    public class TransactionMongoStoreInvocationContext
extends Object
implements MongoStoreInvocationContext
    Invocation context, which has some very basic support for transactions, and is able to cache loaded objects. It always execute all pending update tasks before start searching for other objects It's per-request object (not thread safe)
    Author:
    Marek Posolda
